Can I use a `JSON Schema` in `contributes.configuration` to describe the settings of my extension?

Exaple:
```js
	"configuration": {
		"type": "object",
		"title": "My config",
		"properties": {
			"my.config": {
				"type": [
						"string",
						"object",
						"null"
					],
				"$schema": "./schema/my.config.json",
				"default": null
			}
		}
	}
```
---
http://json-schema.org/example2.html
